    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "## Urban Planning\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to help plan out new features for the city using **text, images, and a city planning report**.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. **Choose an Image**: Select **one of the provided aerial images** of city layouts or **upload an image of a city you are familiar with**.\r\n2. **Select a Planning Document**: Choose **one** of the following to guide your analysis:\r\n   - **City Zoning Guide** - Helps consider land use and regulations.\r\n   - **Transit Report** - Highlights areas needing better accessibility.\r\n   - **Urban Development Plan** - Shows upcoming projects and growth strategies.\r\n3. **Upload Both the Image and the Document**: Attach the **city image and PDF** to your AI Chat.\r\n4. **Copy and Paste the Following Prompt**:\r\n\r\n>Analyze this image and document. What are some possible improvements for **[insert category: transportation, green spaces, zoning, safety, or another of your choice]** in this area? Justify your recommendations based on what you see in the image and data in the document.\r\n\r\n\r\n5. Press **Send** and read AI Chat's response.\r\n6. **Experiment**: Test how AI responds to different inputs:\r\n   - Modify the prompt to **ask AI to justify its response using the document.**\r\n   - Modify your prompt to focus on a different urban feature.\r\n   - Change your input document to see how AI's response shifts.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n**Questions to Consider:**\r\n- How does AI use the PDF information in its response?\r\n- Does it correctly interpret data from the report, or does it make assumptions?\r\n- How does AI's response compare when using **just text and an image** vs **text, image, and a PDF**?\r\n",
